               "text": "<p><center><math displaystyle=\"false\" display=\"block\"><mn>P</mn><mi>=</mi><mn>(x, y)</mn></math></center></p><p><center><math displaystyle=\"false\" display=\"block\"><mn>P</mn><mi>=</mi><mn>(a, b)</mn></math></center></p><p><math displaystyle=\"false\" display=\"block\"><mn>P</mn><mi>=</mi><mn>(c × cos (θ), (c × sin (θ))</mn></math></center></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Formula 4</b>: Representation of the distances walked from the origin <b>O</b> to point <b>P</b>.</p>",
