               "text": "<p><math displaystyle=\"false\" display=\"block\"><mn>P</mn><mi>=</mi><mn>(200, 200)</mn></math></center></p><p class=\"desc\"><b>Formula 5</b>: Representation of the distances traveled from the origin <b>O</b> to point <b>P</b>.</p>",
